    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pasta is cooking, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop <strong>half </strong>your <strong>prosciutto </strong>finely (you'll use the rest later!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
