        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated cheese</strong> with your <strong>cornflour</strong> in a pot and mix until fully combined</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> </strong>250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> to the pot and stir it all together</p><p>Cook over a medium heat for 4-6 min, stirring frequently, or until the cheese has melted and the sauce has thickened slightly</p>",
