    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, remove from the heat</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> to the sauce with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and the <strong>chopped prosciutto</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>croque monsieur sauce</strong></p>",
